  "body": "<div class=\"se-main-container\">\n                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-096ace3c-94c6-40a5-85d6-3322ab09a159\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-099de44a-0b84-4bec-9c6b-b03958aae5ad\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d051b823-69b8-44c3-a628-fe8972e93fbd\"><b>안녕하세요 사당동 한의원, </b></span><span style=\"background-color:#ffef34;\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-6f546da3-d33d-4375-98f1-fd5cc1623f2f\"><b>이수한의원</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs15 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-1083ef34-a3f2-455f-937e-5276b74142cd\"><b> 입니다!</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-096ace3c-94c6-40a5-85d6-3322ab09a159\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-sticker se-l-default\" id=\"SE-54ff0c45-e28d-4e40-be68-421a80926229\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-sticker se-section-align-center se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-sticker\">\n                                <a href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" class=\"__se_sticker_link __se_link\" data-linktype=\"sticker\" data-linkdata='{\"src\" : \"\", \"packCode\" : \"motion2d_01\", \"seq\" : \"11\", \"width\" : \"\", \"height\" : \"\"}'>\n                                    <img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/motion2d_01/original_11.png?type=p100_100\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-sticker-image\" />\n                                </a>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-8bb4cbe0-226c-495d-8581-62658616667f\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-0851f89b-6782-4eb0-8fe8-fb348150d513\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8c043a87-1c8e-4b0c-b09d-41a0a628cca3\"><b>​</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5039fdeb-fdc5-4daa-bcb2-9e47b6226604\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-3cd26731-d3eb-470a-a302-12b310b0fd28\">밤마다 뒤척이며 잠 못 드는 일이 반복된다면, </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-06b2d04e-9ba0-45cf-b2c0-1a6fd06167fa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-73d9a623-c316-4181-84fd-9bd804f72947\">몸에서 보내는 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-08c3b6e3-4a47-4ecd-a5f7-f9d655f5ea27\"><b>신호를 제대로 읽어야 할 때</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-a9bacf1b-5602-42ef-ab80-a20ed9a6cb81\">입니다. 한의학에서는 단순한 수면제보다,  </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b67e1308-63a3-4ba8-91ca-d8f2978d93e7\"><b>몸의 순환을 도와 수면을 유도하는 자연스러운 방법</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-0ac60321-fed8-4986-93d5-0a476f5da28b\">을 </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2f8f098f-77ec-4ed1-845a-d33c6dc22ee9\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-88a8e096-20a5-4904-bbf4-780de12c2773\">중요하게 생각합니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-dd7bcecc-8b3e-44c1-84af-d48cadded76f\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-90d8012d-17b7-4977-a3b0-91205be22155\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-3cdf85dc-fce1-426a-a939-513ed5a84dfa\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7e2f1541-94e4-4bed-83b1-c52d6da8e6cf\">그중 하나가 바로 지압(지압요법)입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-15506177-9c2c-4840-bae8-46b00f4274ae\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b83d74d6-76de-4484-9957-66bfac71d5f9\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b1618355-aa0a-4bf3-b6b8-910d49d3ca50\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-dde30207-a364-4e9e-be69-342ee67542f1\"><b> 불면증에 도움이 되는 지압법, 이수한의원이 알려드립니다</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-8bb4cbe0-226c-495d-8581-62658616667f\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-91611da4-57d9-4546-9dbe-d75fe82d173c\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-91611da4-57d9-4546-9dbe-d75fe82d173c\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ff5d1faa52a7d59e.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1600\", \"originalHeight\" : \"1600\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ff5d1faa52a7d59e.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/ff5d1faa52a7d59e.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"500\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-91611da4-57d9-4546-9dbe-d75fe82d173c\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-9fd7a412-6c76-4d84-acdd-6410a8c5c04a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-center\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-267b4f48-79b6-413d-a391-9f64b3edd8d5\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-acf68933-3de5-4571-b064-f6100360da59\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-e53f44a4-7b2c-4885-a353-2e2e46903f0c\"><b> 지압이 왜 도움이 될까요?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-f3890dbe-671c-41e0-b700-52fc7da13568\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8086f018-a261-4ba6-8625-ec14a642eef1\">불면증은 단순히 ‘잠이 안 오는 증상’이 아니라,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4377da39-6f45-4297-a2de-7b8160eff39d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f8b10754-0a81-4890-9868-fc8fc26ddb26\">✔ </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-20bec810-c085-4975-a728-b201f46224f0\"><b>기혈순환의 장애</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-434d1a90-1c38-4bc8-93b4-e3424e32b518\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-056eaa93-239b-45f9-bcce-1dfc31cff56d\">✔ </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-396b00b1-8398-419d-b419-d6faaf033e6e\"><b>스트레스와 긴장</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-8d93a80f-6741-4719-b523-513f019c590e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b8a4c264-8d7c-4dc0-9a41-41412feca862\">✔ </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-924e52a6-33e8-491a-a43f-65cba13eb64c\"><b>자율신경계의 불균형</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-3c99f2a7-126a-4abf-87ee-f6007d058bea\"> 등에서 비롯될 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-026e4c03-f60e-43ef-8c21-a9665b0ac818\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-ae864fec-a617-4275-a3c1-d4a8157c096c\">특정 부위를 눌러주는 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-309c080c-a48f-40ed-8aad-91e8081ca3e9\"><b>지압법은 기혈의 흐름을 도와 뇌와 몸을 이완시키고</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c4b2b342-7da3-4b19-bc86-76a7f3dcd1b5\">,</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9741c8c1-c3d1-4404-a9e8-950bf16d9667\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-2d6d3cad-fccc-443d-a28e-0cceaa104447\">자연스럽게 수면을 유도할 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-267b4f48-79b6-413d-a391-9f64b3edd8d5\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-0d8d65a7-0971-4b82-9792-399257d7cc72\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-center\" >\n                                <div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" style=\"\" onclick=\"return false;\" data-linktype=\"img\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-0d8d65a7-0971-4b82-9792-399257d7cc72\", \"src\" : \"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/92c3ac1a56783f9c.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"1024\", \"originalHeight\" : \"870\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}'>\n                                        <img src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/92c3ac1a56783f9c.png\" data-lazy-src=\"https://isuhani-clinic-data.s3.ap-northeast-2.amazonaws.com/images/legacy/92c3ac1a56783f9c.png\" data-width=\"500\" data-height=\"424\" alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" />\n                                    </a>\n                                </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_image\", \"id\": \"SE-0d8d65a7-0971-4b82-9792-399257d7cc72\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"image\", \"ai\": \"false\" }}'></script>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-8dc96297-8a16-46ef-8d5d-b0b937c1a67a\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-center\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-c3f40404-b105-40df-ab4a-d70441f75153\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-b39268f4-034f-4c39-b77c-7ea194a6fe3a\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-04097a33-b35f-4fc5-ac52-8a8d46bd502b\"><b>🖐 불면증에 좋은 대표적인 지압점 3가지</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-80180740-9a8d-40e5-a090-b03a4d2246c0\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9f887cd4-1af9-459f-9ad9-1165099130bc\"><b>1. 신문혈(神門穴) – 마음을 진정시키는 혈</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-6da2e010-0bb7-4284-8228-adf760d9237d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-46854336-ab1d-493c-8db2-3a7695acb341\"><b>위치</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-adf1e22b-761a-4e74-bc52-db5e0b3f2d2b\">: 손목 안쪽, 새끼손가락 쪽 손목 주름의 끝</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-69e59787-d43a-4a64-ad0a-c27555eb508b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b4c0c23b-3fa8-4644-b39f-edb65733ff99\"><b>효과</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-6974ca00-fc42-4623-bb58-da853183b120\">: 불안, 초조, 마음이 가라앉지 않을 때 추천</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4b201a0e-e73c-44fd-a972-781e3bc52210\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d4b3554f-27b0-46a7-a982-a6dd11f7c072\"><b>지압법</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-5109d2d2-d4a3-4ecf-a0a8-a2064f56b62c\">: 엄지손가락으로 5초간 지그시 눌렀다가 천천히 놓기, 5회 반복</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-2484ecf0-b155-494b-928f-3404e5b80ef5\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-b83f7131-77e1-44ec-909d-e2a0792b7241\"><b>2. 백회혈(百會穴) – 머리를 맑게 하고 긴장을 푸는 혈</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-271699a5-05bc-441a-92c6-c16267e489db\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-7fa43985-6146-4021-9a91-912fc9973775\"><b>위치</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-c4d659b2-b7f5-482d-ac13-8904c07513aa\">: 정수리 중앙, 양 귀를 연결한 선과 머리 정중앙이 만나는 지점</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-53b487d0-df1b-457a-ad3f-8aeefbbe738e\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-9db331e4-c549-4ff2-b269-4f6c92eeeec2\"><b>효과</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8bed099f-d711-4a33-84b9-403cb3f96ecc\">: 머리가 무겁거나 생각이 많을 때, 자율신경 안정</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-dcae2d66-2572-4ce3-af71-90706d319fbe\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-799765ca-ae48-4f77-a047-c1a4659584ec\"><b>지압법</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-0aad89fd-b342-4a84-96e5-544d18fdd4fd\">: 가볍게 원을 그리듯 눌러주기 (1~2분)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-5c6ace6c-8bd1-46a9-a499-c7045d23663b\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-24955d3f-4dde-4497-bc11-5b06e67be87e\"><b>3. 용천혈(湧泉穴) – 땅과 연결되는 에너지의 시작점</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9f1da80d-b679-4710-ab3b-02d5c85bd504\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-2823c1e2-8298-4baf-9c5a-f33424f72b06\"><b>위치</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f485025b-e556-4e21-9096-68b1d7d631a5\">: 발바닥의 움푹 들어간 부분 (발가락 아래 1/3 지점)</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-78e7c971-3456-414e-8bd4-c9af9fcbb79d\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-bef9c095-274f-4b1f-a8db-397862aeb24f\"><b>효과</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-35debe08-1833-4dc1-87cd-30e881584cd6\">: 기운을 아래로 내려주고, 마음을 가라앉혀 숙면 유도</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align- \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-49b7b495-fd6d-4b97-a76e-e2349aacff04\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-f55b7639-8abe-4586-af00-9f9a330eddab\"><b>지압법</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-27a13c59-6f17-44c6-bdc1-2ad40b4c4f55\">: 손가락이나 지압봉으로 좌우 1~2분씩 눌러주기</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-c3f40404-b105-40df-ab4a-d70441f75153\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line1\" id=\"SE-bea6a30a-690f-4b99-b7ee-4f5d6d7aa39d\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line1 se-section-align-center\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n                                <hr class=\"se-hr\" />\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-94855735-d766-4cad-a207-24dda0380f48\">\n                    <div class=\"se-component-content\">\n                        <div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n                            <div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n                                    <!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-4483934f-7c2d-4a3b-b4e6-eac7f00bc3fd\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-a04280e1-1c64-4623-8f2f-27568967c4d4\"><b>지압할 때 이것만 기억하세요</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-74f576a8-c7a5-4118-9f36-6089af95031c\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-61aa9403-84f3-4535-ab22-b5348dd4e863\"><b>자기 전 30분 전</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-bee54851-5961-4b26-8a65-c5e644750279\">, 조용한 분위기에서 지압을 해보세요.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-d1cc1b8e-b179-461b-b003-d1b62182c199\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-59a68815-e8d1-4969-9800-fde9aef360cb\">손을 따뜻하게 한 후 누르면 </span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-8d6ea522-c0f4-460d-9715-cdad0717ef6e\"><b>이완 효과가 배가</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-5cab5117-e23b-4574-8763-467c9cfdf9e7\">됩니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-54ef5f8b-0005-42f6-a612-cd5eeccf8eca\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-32d61b6b-aefb-4d58-b148-1a254358c7ff\"><b>무리하게 세게 누를 필요는 없습니다.</b></span><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-d0f43a39-48a7-4d25-9a01-edc9bdc50200\"> </span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-center \" style=\"\" id=\"SE-9130eaec-298c-4f96-8212-913fc2c7ca63\"><span style=\"\" class=\"se-fs- se-ff-system   \" id=\"SE-0d546356-7a61-4201-957c-cbc7fa031d19\">오히려 부드럽게 눌러주는 것이 더 효과적입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <script type=\"text/data\" class=\"__se_module_data\" data-module-v2='{\"type\": \"v2_text\", \"id\": \"SE-94855735-d766-4cad-a207-24dda0380f48\", \"data\": {\"ctype\": \"text\"  }}'></script>\n                </div>                <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n                